"Forgetting who's in charge again, I see," Gatara snorts.  "I'll 
forgive it this time.  Riekan!"

"Yes?"  The greyish-blue Rogue still seems disinterested, but Gatara 
doesn't appear to notice.

"Go make the necessary preparations.  Predacon, if you try anything I 
don't like, it comes out of HER hide, got it?"
